    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/85251aef037b83bda907bdcebfaae351.webp?t=1747339909\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras_big/85251aef037b83bda907bdcebfaae351.avif?t=1747339909 width=800 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forge your destiny in Star Life, a space-based economic &amp; strategic RPG simulation. Begin as a humble newcomer on a vibrant alien planet, scraping by with basic jobs or petty crime. Through skillful planning, strategic resource management, and a healthy (or not) dose of risk-taking, climb the economic ladder, mastering skills in a dynamic learn-by-doing system. Will you rise from obscurity to become a galactic tycoon, having enough power to overcome those who led you there?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/c398520b7149d791b0c0471247f4c75a.poster.avif?t=1747339909\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/c398520b7149d791b0c0471247f4c75a.webm?t=1747339909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/c398520b7149d791b0c0471247f4c75a.mp4?t=1747339909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/eaba50014de16d51ec4e6b2305a779e9.avif?t=1747339909\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras_big/eaba50014de16d51ec4e6b2305a779e9.avif?t=1747339909 width=800 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision carries weight. Mine asteroids, plunder unsuspecting freighters, and engage in lucrative trade across solar system. Each choice has consequences, and mistakes can be fatal. Command your spaceship, manage your resources, and navigate dangerous space . Too dangerous for you? Live a normal life on any planet, until consequences of peaceful life hit hard like a rock.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/7c4adeb7ae6d6bdb9526741c4c4fa4c6.poster.avif?t=1747339909\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/7c4adeb7ae6d6bdb9526741c4c4fa4c6.webm?t=1747339909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/7c4adeb7ae6d6bdb9526741c4c4fa4c6.mp4?t=1747339909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/b06980f539777dc626bccb025a3fcf44.webp?t=1747339909\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras_big/b06980f539777dc626bccb025a3fcf44.avif?t=1747339909 width=800 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > For more repetitive tasks utilize the Life Planner to  schedule your actions, optimizing your routines for maximum efficiency. Build enterprises, master skills, and grow your wealth on the planet until you are ready to conquer space. Every day is a step toward your ultimate goal, which, funny enough - you do not know.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/1020c936190153ce79aaa35ed4a19ab5.poster.avif?t=1747339909\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/1020c936190153ce79aaa35ed4a19ab5.webm?t=1747339909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/1020c936190153ce79aaa35ed4a19ab5.mp4?t=1747339909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/ac1913b016df747d57d3de4027d2c664.webp?t=1747339909\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras_big/ac1913b016df747d57d3de4027d2c664.avif?t=1747339909 width=800 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This single-player sandbox offers unparalleled freedom. Manipulate markets, build new industries, conquer planets, or choose a life of quiet contemplation, focusing on personal growth and community building. Your choices shape the destiny of a solar system. Which path will you choose?<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/67fd417892c95d88fda9c0a504a4ebd9.poster.avif?t=1747339909\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/67fd417892c95d88fda9c0a504a4ebd9.webm?t=1747339909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305980/extras/67fd417892c95d88fda9c0a504a4ebd9.mp4?t=1747339909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
